values.value: THIS PROCEDURE CODE IS DENIED. THIS SERVICE WAS PERFORMED IN A FACILITY SETTING AND IS NOT ELIGIBLE FOR SEPARATE REIMBURSEMENT TO THE PROVIDER. IF YOU USED A NETWORK PROVIDER, YOU DON'T OWE ANYTHING. IF YOU RECEIVE A BILL FROM AN OUT-OF-NETWORK PROVIDER FOR THESE SERVICES, PLEASE CALL THE NUMBER ON YOUR HEALTH PLAN ID CARD.
